    "body": "I can't see anywhere that the updated enr ever actually gets published by the discovery code.  If another peer asks for our enr, we'll give the updated record, but nothing actively notifies the network of the change. And importantly, nothing updates our own record in the peer table so it would be the old version that gets sent in response to find requests.",
